&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>If someone asks us, who are you? &lt;br>
Or we ask ourselves, who am I? &lt;br>
Or we ask someone, who are you? &lt;br>
What answer do we expect from others? &lt;br>
Or what answer do we give them?&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Depending upon the context and situation &lt;br>
the answer can vary but if you analyze the answer &lt;br>
then you will find the answer is referring &lt;br>
to objects and concepts around the answerer.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>